16:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekiston Markaziy bankining kalit stavkasi yillik 14% ni tashkil etadi, bu tijorat banklarining kredit stavkalari uchun asos yaratadi. iste'mol kreditlari bo'yicha o'rtacha stavkalar bank, kredit muddati va qarz oluvchining kredit tarixiga qarab yillik 22% dan 33% gacha o'zgaradi. Kredit kalkulyatori annuitet yoki differentsial to'lov sxemasi bo'yicha oylik to'lov, umumiy to'lovlar summasi va ortiqcha to'lovni hisoblaydi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Annuitet to'lov — har oy bir xil summa. Formula: OT = S × (r × (1+r)^n) / ((1+r)^n − 1), bunda S — kredit summasi, r — oylik stavka (yillik/12), n — oylar soni. Differentsial to'lov — kamayib boruvchi, chunki foizlar qoldiq qarzga hisoblanadi. Annuitet byudjetni rejalashtirish uchun qulayroq, differentsial sxema umumiy ortiqcha to'lov bo'yicha foydaliroq."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Hisoblash misoli: 50 000 000 so'mlik kredit 3 yilga (36 oy) yillik 22% da. Annuitet to'lov: oylik stavka = 1,833%, oylik to'lov ≈ 1 920 000 so'm, umumiy to'lovlar ≈ 69 120 000 so'm, ortiqcha to'lov ≈ 19 120 000 so'm (38,2%). Differentsial sxemada: birinchi to'lov ≈ 2 306 000 so'm, oxirgi ≈ 1 414 000 so'm, ortiqcha to'lov ≈ 17 028 000 so'm (34,1%)."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Kredit rasmiylashtirishda banklar qarz oluvchining to'lov qobiliyatini hisobga oladi: oylik to'lov sof daromadning 50% dan oshmasligi kerak. Talab qilinadigan hujjatlar: pasport, daromad to'g'risida ma'lumotnoma, kredit tarixi. Ta'minot — kafil, mulk garovi yoki garovsiz (bank ish haqi mijozlari uchun)."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistonda kreditni muddatidan oldin to'lash 2020-yildan boshlab jarimasisz ruxsat etilgan. Muddatidan oldin to'laganda foizlar qayta hisoblanadi — siz faqat kreditdan haqiqiy foydalanish muddati uchun to'laysiz. Mavjud kreditni pastroq stavkada qayta moliyalash MB kalit stavkasi pasayganida foydali bo'lishi mumkin."}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 space-y-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-foreground","children":"Ma'lumotnoma va tariflar"}],[["$","div","0",{"className":"overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-border","children":["$","table",null,{"className":"w-full text-sm","children":[["$","caption",null,{"className":"px-4 py-2 text-left font-medium text-foreground bg-muted/50 border-b border-border","children":"O'zbekiston banklarida iste'mol kredit stavkalari"}],"$L1c","$L1d"]}]}]]]}],"$L1e","$L1f"]}]
